OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRussia's new schoolbook    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Faims to justify Ukraine war
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Authorities in Moscow have unveiled a  
OL,6, new schoolbook which aims to justify   
OL,7, the war on Ukraine and accuses the West
OL,8, of trying to destroy Russia.           
OL,10,FAccording to excerpts published by     
OL,11,FRussian media, schoolchildren will now 
OL,12,Fbe taught that human civilisation could
OL,13,Fhave come to an end had Vladimir Putin 
OL,14,Fnot started his "special military      
OL,15,Foperation" against Ukraine.            
OL,17,FThe textbook, called "Russian History, 
OL,18,F1945 - early 21st century", was        
OL,19,Fco-authored by presidential adviser    
OL,20,FVladimir Medinsky, formerly Russian    
OL,21,Fculture minister.                      
